      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The ideal consumer for a truly exclusive, high-end watch brand is typically a globally successful individual who values heritage and discreet luxury over flashy displays. They are often established professionals, entrepreneurs, or inheritors from old money backgrounds, possessing a refined taste cultivated through international travel and elite social circles. While their cultural background is diverse, the core demographic often aligns with those who appreciate meticulous craftsmanship and a quiet confidence, rather than overt displays of wealth. Focusing on their appreciation for legacy and subtle status signals will be far more effective than targeting specific ethnic groups.",
